---
title: Mexican Beef & Rice Bowl with Creamy Corn Slaw & Cheddar
description: Yes, we’re putting everything in a bowl tonight, how else are we to contain this much yumminess? So, let’s add basmati rice and spiced beef mince, creamy slaw and shredded Cheddar cheese for those Mexican-style vibes. Go ahead and lick the bowl clean when you’re done!
